      <title>贝莱德的沃森认为固定收益领域存在巨大机遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-05/blackrock-s-watson-huge-opportunities-in-fixed-income-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球基本固定收益策略主管玛丽莲·沃森 (Marilyn Watson) 预计利率将继续高于市场预期。沃森在彭博电视上还讨论了她投资债券市场的策略。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-05/blackrock-s-watson-huge-opportunities-in-fixed-income-video</guid>
