    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚计划暂停征收食品进口税以缓解通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/nigeria-plans-to-suspend-import-levies-on-food-to-ease-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚正考虑暂停对主食、药品和其他必需品的进口关税六个月，以减缓这个非洲人口第一大国的通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/nigeria-plans-to-suspend-import-levies-on-food-to-ease-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国财政部长承诺减税 250 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/germany-s-finance-minister-promises-tax-cuts-worth-25-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 宣布，到 2026 年，将为家庭减免 230 亿欧元（250 亿美元）的所得税，与此同时，他正与执政联盟伙伴争论如何填补明年的预算漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/germany-s-finance-minister-promises-tax-cuts-worth-25-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:23:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北海油田 Buzzard 仍处于关闭状态，有助于缓解供应过剩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/north-sea-oil-field-buzzard-still-shut-helping-to-ease-glut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北海福尔蒂斯原油最大供给油田布扎德的意外关闭令许多交易商感到意外，并可能有助于缓解供应过剩的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/north-sea-oil-field-buzzard-still-shut-helping-to-ease-glut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地中海地区野火风险达到极端水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/wildfire-risk-reaches-extreme-levels-across-mediterranean</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊和西班牙的野火威胁已达到极端程度，风险也蔓延至法国里维埃拉。]]></description>
